{"data":[{"date":"15:26 16/07","title":"H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1c th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Pogba \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/hanh-dong-khac-thuong-cua-pogba-o-chung-ket-world-cup-2018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1c th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p th\u1eafng Croatia 4-2.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa Pogba l\u1ea1i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018. Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Croatia, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 qua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Rakitic v\u00e0 Luka Modric m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Pogba c\u00f2n ghi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng, gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 4-2 chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh C\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 h\u01b0\u1edbng l\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i s\u00e2n Luznhiki v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ed7 tay v\u00e0o ng\u1ef1c, k\u1ec1 tay v\u00e0o tai nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 mu\u1ed1n l\u1eafng nghe \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c xua tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00fai ch\u00e0o NHM \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Pogba l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u00e0 NHM Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup. S\u1ed1 l\u00e0, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup di\u1ec5n ra, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb NHM c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed3i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man United v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a Les Bleus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00e1i v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ed3i s\u1ee5t \u1edf Man United, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 \u1edf World Cup v\u00e0 l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i qu\u00e1n qu\u00e2n.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/180716_030332_426.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/180716_030302_99.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/180716_030232_238.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/180716_030201_713.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/180716_030138_55.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4266","checkdouble":"191353"},{"date":"17:43 16/07","title":"Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \"tr\u1ea5n y\u1ec3m\" s\u00e2n Luznhiki tr\u01b0\u1edbc chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018?","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/phap-da-tran-yem-san-luznhiki-truoc-chung-ket-world-cup-2018.png","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4265","checkdouble":"191354"},{"date":"15:40 16/07","title":"Ch\u00e2n dung n\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Croatia","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/chan-dung-nu-tong-thong-ham-mo-bong-da-cua-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn khi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2>N\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Croatia Kolinda Grabar-Kitarovic tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd khi m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n Nga.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00e2n dung n\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Croatia h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 cu\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00e2n dung n\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Croatia h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 cu\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/pre3-7708-1531709883.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">N\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Croatia Kolinda Grabar-Kitarovic \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n nh\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Nga h\u00f4m 8/7. \u1ea2nh: AFP.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo NDTV, n\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng 50 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 bay v\u00e9 h\u1ea1ng ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 nh\u1ea3y c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng sau khi Croatia th\u1eafng Nga. B\u00e0 Grabar-Kitarovic th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fac m\u1eebng v\u00e0 \u00f4m c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <br>\r\nN\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u00fac m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Croatia<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1i 15/7, sau khi Croatia thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-4 \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, n\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng xinh \u0111\u1eb9p ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u00e2u \u0111\u1eadm trong l\u00f2ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 khi \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a, \u00f4m v\u00e0 an \u1ee7i t\u1eebng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0 c\u0169ng vui v\u1ebb \u00f4m T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Ph\u00e1p Emmanuel Macron \u0111\u1ec3 chia vui sau khi tuy\u1ec3n Croatia ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. C\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh x\u1eed th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 thi\u1ec7n ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a b\u00e0 Grabar-Kitarovic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9. H\u1ecd nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 thao th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tong thong Croatia lau nuoc mat cho thu quan Luka Modric sau khi doi Croatia thua Phap o chung ket World Cup toi qua. Anh: RT.\" title=\"T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Croatia lau n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft cho th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Luka Modric sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i Croatia thua Ph\u00e1p \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup t\u1ed1i qua. \u1ea2nh: RT.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/modric-2125-1531712702.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Croatia lau n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft cho th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Luka Modric sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i Croatia thua Ph\u00e1p \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup t\u1ed1i qua. \u1ea2nh: RT.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Sun, b\u00e0 Grabar-Kitarovic sinh ng\u00e0y 29/4/1968 \u1edf v\u00f9ng Yugoslavia, Croatia. B\u00e0 t\u1eebng \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd tham gia ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh trao \u0111\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc sinh trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n \u0111i h\u1ecdc, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng trung h\u1ecdc Los Alamos \u1edf bang New Mexico, M\u1ef9. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng 50 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Zagreb (Croatia), Vienna (\u00c1o), Washington DC (M\u1ef9). B\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u th\u1ea1c s\u0129 t\u1ea1i Croatia c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ba n\u0103m. B\u00e0 n\u00f3i th\u00e0nh th\u1ea1o ti\u1ebfng Croatia, ti\u1ebfng Anh, T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3. B\u00e0 c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat ti\u1ebfng \u0110\u1ee9c, Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Italy. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1eebng nh\u1ea7m n\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu Coco Austin v\u00e0 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean M\u1ef9 Diamond Foxx do b\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGrabar-Kitarovic tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Croatia th\u00e1ng 2/2015 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u1eef t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a qu\u1ed1c gia h\u01a1n 4 tri\u1ec7u d\u00e2n n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, b\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c nhau khi tham gia \u0111\u1ea3ng Li\u00ean minh D\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 Croatia (HDZ) n\u0103m 1993, b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n cho b\u1ed9 Ngo\u1ea1i giao.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ba Grabar-Kitarovic tren chuyen bay cung cac co dong vien Croatia sang Nga de co vu doi nha. Anh: Facebook.\" title=\"B\u00e0 Grabar-Kitarovic tr\u00ean chuy\u1ebfn bay c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Croatia sang Nga \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u1ea2nh: Facebook.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/pre1-8984-1531709884.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u00e0 Grabar-Kitarovic tr\u00ean chuy\u1ebfn bay c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Croatia sang Nga \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u1ea2nh: Facebook.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0 Grabar-Kitarovic quay tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Croatia v\u00e0 tham gia v\u00e0o qu\u1ed1c h\u1ed9i sau th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ebfn Washington DC nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00e0m t\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng, b\u00e0 gi\u1eef ch\u1ee9c \u0110\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 Croatia \u1edf M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd NATO. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0 Kolinda Grabar-Kitarovic k\u1ebft h\u00f4n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng Jakov Kitarovic n\u0103m 1996 v\u00e0 sinh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai con. Con g\u00e1i l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a b\u00e0 Katarina, 17 tu\u1ed5i, l\u00e0 v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u0103ng ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt, c\u00f2n con trai Luka sinh n\u0103m 2003. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ngoisao.net<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4264","checkdouble":"191355"},{"date":"16:42 16/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/nhung-hinh-anh-dau-tien-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; colo