m tra y t\u1ebf.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac CDV Juventus den tu rat som de chao don Ronaldo.\" title=\"C\u00e1c C\u0110V Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Ronaldo.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/FBL-ITA-SERIEA-JUVENTUS-RONALDO-(1).jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c C\u0110V Juventus \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Ronaldo.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo du kien se chinh thuc ra mat sau khi hoan tat cuoc kiem tra y te.\" title=\"Ronaldo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/FBL-ITA-SERIEA-JUVENTUS-RONALDO.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo khong quen tao dang truoc cac ong kinh truyen thong truoc khi di chuyen den dia diem kiem tra y te.\" title=\"Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/croatia-dau-do-bong-dang-u23-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo va gia dinh cung toi Juvunetus - doi bong danh dau mot chuong moi trong su nghiep.\" title=\"Ronaldo v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng t\u1edbi Juvunetus - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Juventus-New-Signing-Cristiano-Ronaldo-Arrives-In-turin-(1).jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng t\u1edbi Juvunetus - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/nhung-hinh-anh-dau-tien-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Cristiano Ronaldo b\u01b0\u1edbc xu\u1ed1ng m\u00e1y bay khi t\u1edbi Juventus ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1\u00a0Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-roi-real-180-191352.html\">Kaka l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/de-ronaldo-ra-di-la-sai-lam-lon-nhat-trong-lich-su-cua-real-madrid-180-191345.html\">\u0110\u1ec3 Ronaldo ra \u0111i l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-suyt-toi-napoli-thay-vi-juventus-176-191263.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Ronaldo \u0111\u00fang ra \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi Napoli thay v\u00ec Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-va-benzema-sap-doi-dau-nhau-o-serie-a-176-191165.html\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Benzema s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau \u1edf Serie A?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muon-oai-ronaldo-juventus-tinh-tai-hop-pogba-176-191121.html\">M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus t\u00ednh t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/kevin-strootman-khong-ngai-doi-dau-ronaldo-tai-serie-a-176-191088.html\">Sao Roma kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4263","checkdouble":"191363"},{"date":"12:07 16/07","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 19 V-League: Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/15/du-am-vong-19-vleague-nhung-chien-thang-xung-dang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HAGL, SLNA v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 CLB TP.HCM \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.</h2><h2>1. HAGL t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u00f9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Pleiku g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n To\u00e0n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf m\u00e0n cho chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a HAGL b\u1eb1ng pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c ngay nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u00edt th\u1ea5y \u1edf ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o qu\u00ea H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o g\u00f3c xa khung th\u00e0nh, trong s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 T\u00f4 V\u0129nh L\u1ee3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y khi nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, ho\u1eb7c \u0111i thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, ho\u1eb7c b\u1ecb x\u00e0 ngang t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 19 V-League Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m v\u00f2ng 19 V-League Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/aGFnbF9jb25ncGh1b25nX2FubXVuZw==.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, HAGL v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 Osmar v\u00e0 V\u0103n Anh \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c 3-1 cho &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo;. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League gi\u00fap HAGL c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean BXH, tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. SLNA ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ea1ch th\u1eafng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea1ch th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a SLNA v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf con s\u1ed1 6 khi h\u1ecd v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c Nasciment s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tri\u1ec3n khai c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Cao Xu\u00e2n Th\u1eafng&nbsp;\u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 42, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Olaha \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c 2-1 sau pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 53 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u1edf v\u00f2ng 19, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o top 4 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi 29 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 12 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u00cdt ai ng\u1edd r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng l\u1ea1i v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa &lsquo;c\u01a1n kh\u00e1t&rsquo; c\u1ee7a TP.HCM<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng 19 V-League v\u1eeba di\u1ec5n ra, CLB TP.HCM \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 &lsquo;qu\u00fd h\u01a1n v\u00e0ng&rsquo; tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Miura ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Christian v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f3 c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf ph\u00fat 23 v\u00e0 26 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 an to\u00e0n cho \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng th\u00ec s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd sau \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap TP.HCM l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2, qua \u0111\u00f3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac chu\u1ed7i 13 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua. Tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 TP.HCM trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TP.HCM vs Da Nang\" title=\"TP.HCM vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/1531637049.jpg\" /></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB TP.HCM xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh su\u00fdt t\u1ea1o c\u00fa s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH, CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 19 V-League, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u1ebf, v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t hay v\u00e0 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1edbi 3-0 sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Diogo v\u00e0 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a V\u0169 Th\u1ebf V\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ha Noi vs Nam Dinh\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/1531703815.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn th\u1ee7y chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9ng l\u00ean m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 l\u1ea1i 3 b\u00e0n do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a &lsquo;h\u00fa h\u1ed3n&rsquo;. Ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby, \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9. Nh\u01b0ng d\u1eabu sao \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 12 tr\u00ean BXH. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01a1 t\u1edbi v\u00e9 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00f2ng 19 V-League c\u00f2n ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1 trong c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa FLC Thanh H\u00f3a vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00e0 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i gi\u1eefa Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n r\u00fat ng\u1eafn kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 14 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ngo\u1ea1i binh r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH sau vong 19 V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH sau v\u00f2ng 19 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/BXH-vong-19.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>BXH sau v\u00f2ng 19 V-League 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/slna-toan-thang-7-tran-lien-tiep-hlv-nguyen-duc-thang-bi-soc-168-191332.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/slna-toan-thang-7-tran-lien-tiep-hlv-nguyen-duc-thang-bi-soc.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/slna-toan-thang-7-tran-lien-tiep-hlv-nguyen-duc-thang-bi-soc-168-191332.html\">HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c khi SLNA to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 7 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp</span><br />\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-roi-chien-thang-truoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-191331.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/danh-roi-chien-thang-truoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-roi-chien-thang-truoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi-168-191331.html\">\u0110\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-cua-hagl-truoc-can-tho-168-191193.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-cua-hagl-truoc-can-tho.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-cua-hagl-truoc-can-tho-168-191193.html\">HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1?</span><br />\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4262","checkdouble":"191338"},{"date":"17:07 16/07","title":"Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Bayern Munich c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1eddi bi\u1ebft \u01a1n Guardiola","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/16/alaba-phat-bieu-ve-guardiola-va-thoi-gian-o-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>David Alaba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Guardiola, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng c\u00f3 3 n\u0103m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c chung v\u1edbi anh t\u1ea1i Bayern Munich. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111a n\u0103ng n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1edd c\u00f3 Guardiola, anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p m\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Guardiola \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi Alaba</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pep Guardiola t\u1eebng c\u00f3 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bayern Munich (n\u0103m 2013 t\u1edbi 2016). Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga, 2 c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia c\u00f9ng H\u00f9m x\u00e1m trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 ngai v\u00e0ng Champions League \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea3ng tr\u00e1nh th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Guardiola th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng Pep \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Bayern v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c khuy\u1ebft \u0111i danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea7m ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, David Alaba l\u1ea1i ngh\u0129 kh\u00e1c. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c1o h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i th\u1ea7y c\u0169, ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh tin l\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Alaba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Guardiola, th\u1ea7y c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Alaba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Guardiola, th\u1ea7y c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/30/David-Alaba-phat-bieu-ve-HLV-Guardiola,-thay-cu-tai-Bayern-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Alaba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Guardiola v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebft \u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, Guardiola r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi t\u00f4i\u201d, Alaba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Guardiola. \u201c\u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00e1c. Nh\u1edd \u00f4ng \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1 theo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGuardiola \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch m\u1edbi, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i Bayern. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may m\u1eafn trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Alaba duoc Bayern dinh gia toi 80 trieu Euro\" title=\"David Alaba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/8/4/Doi-hinh-xuat-sac-nhat-do-Robben-binh-chon-hinh-anh-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Alaba tin th\u1ea7y c\u0169 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Guardiola s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlaba kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi th\u1ea5y Guardiola ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Manchester City. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u00f4ng c\u00f9ng The Citizens gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n. \u201cGuardiola \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf Anh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u00c1o n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cB\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1eafp t\u1edbi, Alaba s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i Guardiola khi Bayern so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Man City trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ng\u00e0y 29/7 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho ra s\u00e2n \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro Cristiano Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 HLV Guardiola tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/pep-guardiola-the-khong-dinh-dang-gi-den-barcelona-nua-180-188217.html\">Pep Guardiola th\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng d\u00ednh d\u00e1ng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn Barcelona n\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/guardiola-phan-hoi-to-cao-cua-toure-172-188186.html\">Guardiola n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi b\u1ecb tr\u00f2 c\u0169 t\u1ed1 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tro-cu-dua-ra-nhan-xet-kho-tin-ve-mourinho-va-guardiola-172-188015.html\">Tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t kh\u00f3 tin v\u1ec1 Mourinho v\u00e0 Guardiola</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/neymar-tha-thinh-man-city-pep-van-rat-tinh-don-172-187954.html\">Neymar \u201cth\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\u201d Man City, Pep v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u1ec9nh \u0111\u00f2n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/yaya-toure-vs-pep-guardiola-nguoi-man-city-dung-ve-phia-ai-172-187848.html\">Yaya Toure vs Pep Guardiola: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda ai?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4261","checkdouble":"191364"},{"date":"12:55 16/07","title":"Barca mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/17/barca-muon-vuot-mat-arsenal-vu-tien-ve-nzonzi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Sevilla</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-barca-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-hau-ve-clement-lenglet-180-191060.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca mua Clement Lenglet </span>c\u1ee7a Sevilla th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Sau khi c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Sevilla.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/17/barca-muon-vuot-mat-arsenal-vu-tien-ve-nzonzi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Steven NZonzi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Steven Nzonzi c\u1ee7a Sevilla \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Iniesta chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f2n Paulinho tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c khi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Barca m\u1ecfng \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi PSG h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Adrien Rabiot, Barca cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Valverde \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Nzonzi v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Camp Nou, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf La Liga c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Nzonzi duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 to\u00e0n n\u0103ng khi v\u1eeba c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Barca s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nzonzi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 v\u1edbi Sevilla s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, sau 3 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Sevilla, Nzonzi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, anh mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Barca s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"NZonzi da hong penalty o tran Sevilla 0-2 Leicester\" title=\"NZonzi da hong penalty o tran Sevilla 0-2 Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/3/15/Nhung-nguoi-hung-va-toi-do-o-tran-dau-Leicester-2-0-Sevilla-hinh-anh-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 NZonzi\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal \u0111ang nh\u1eafm Nzonzi \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 HLV Emery \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf Sevilla, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates. Arsenal c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 Nzonzi, b\u1edfi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a. Xhaka ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u00e2ng l\u00ean t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Nzonzi \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Sevilla, cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa Arsenal v\u00e0 Barca h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4260","checkdouble":"191340"},{"date":"15:08 16/07","title":"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-world-cup-2018-co-the-tro-lai-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Luka Modric r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, hi\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf Anh theo \u0111u\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea v\u00e0 Liverpool theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Modric</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1985 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Toni Kroos t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m hay nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric r\u1eddi Real Madrid tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luka Modric r\u1eddi Real Madrid tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-world-cup-2018-co-the-tro-lai-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea v\u00e0 Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Modric gi\u00fap Real Madrid gi\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. Ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 2-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00e1 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Croatia. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/mbappe-va-modric-duoc-vinh-danh-sau-tran-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-421-191288.html\" target=\"_blank\">Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018</span>, ngo\u00e0i 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00ec anh c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Modric gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh Chelsea v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKlopp \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Modric v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Anfield, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 HLV Sarri c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Modric c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Luka Modric r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, hi\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Modric\" title=\"tien ve Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/real-madrid-da-co-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Modric c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm vinh quang l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Liverpool ho\u1eb7c Chelsea d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Real Madrid nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool ho\u1eb7c Chelsea.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n Chelsea b\u1edfi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Modric r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi The Kop nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4259","checkdouble":"191344"},{"date":"15:11 16/07","title":"\"\u0110\u1ec3 Ronaldo ra \u0111i l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Real Madrid\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/de-ronaldo-ra-di-la-sai-lam-lon-nhat-trong-lich-su-cua-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, c\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real Ramon Calderon cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo sang Juventus l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.</h2><h2>\u0110\u1ec3 Ronaldo sang Juventus l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Real</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u, CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Cristiano Ronaldo sang Juventus. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 112 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo la cau thu dat gia nhat lich su Juventus.\" title=\"Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Juventus.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Real-muon-mua-Rodrigo-ve-thay-Ronaldo,-nguoi-moi-sang-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real, Ramon Calderon ti\u1ebfc khi Ronaldo sang Juventus ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Real \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo sang Juventus \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u trong d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn. C\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00fd ki\u1ebfn \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m khi Real chia tay Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 c\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real, Ramon Calderon c\u0169ng \u0111i theo suy ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3. L\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1ng n\u00ean m\u1ed9t &lsquo;t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00e0i&rsquo; t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Bernabeu, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n v\u1ecb c\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t \u0111au l\u00f2ng khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m F.Perez b\u00e1n Ronaldo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd AS, \u00f4ng Ramon Calderon cho hay: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt bu\u1ed3n khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n Ronaldo. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eebng r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Ronaldo v\u1ec1 Real Madrid khi M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n anh \u1ea5y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e1n Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t, cho d\u00f9 s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 100 tri\u1ec7u hay 1 t\u1ef7. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 1 t\u1ef7 euro \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu anh \u1ea5y v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t. V\u00ec v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n Ronaldo r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed m\u00e0 Real g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Real Madrid sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o tr\u1eafng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a CR7. V\u00e0 th\u1ebf l\u00e0, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1eebng ghi t\u1edbi 44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Los Blancos m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus, n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 5 l\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh QBV th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4258","checkdouble":"191345"},{"date":"15:44 16/07","title":"Kaka l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-roi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real. C\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Los Blancos kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 suy t\u00ednh k\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real Madrid, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha m\u1edbi k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus theo th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCho t\u1edbi l\u00fac ra \u0111i, Ronaldo v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real v\u1edbi 44 b\u00e0n sau 44 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng theo g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u Galatico: Kaka th\u00ec CR7 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 h\u01a1n ai h\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-Ronaldo-roi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Cristiano l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d, Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real tr\u00ean Omnisport. \u201cQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Madrid sang Juventus l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCristiano bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ra \u0111i. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh \u1ea5y ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng: \u2018T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Real v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c\u2019. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn anh \u1ea5y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Juve \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha sang Italia ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng.\u201d <br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho anh m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Kaka cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 Ronaldo. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1edbi s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t hay kh\u00f4ng, c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil n\u00f3i th\u00eam:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo va Kaka\" title=\"Ronaldo va Kaka\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-roi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Kaka khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Cristiano th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem anh \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t may m\u1eafn v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u0169ng may m\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u00f9ng anh \u1ea5y trong 4 n\u0103m.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y Cristiano chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o, m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o, gi\u00e0u kh\u00e1t khao \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd ra sao. Anh \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00e1c. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Cristiano s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/spalletti-so-sanh-perisic-voi-ronaldo-421-191163.html\">Sao Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/tay-ban-nha-doa-bat-ronaldo-tai-italia-188-191161.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1ecda b\u1eaft Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Italia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muon-oai-ronaldo-juventus-tinh-tai-hop-pogba-176-191121.html\">M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus t\u00ednh t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-rodrigo-ve-thay-ronaldo-180-191111.html\">Real mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/kevin-strootman-khong-ngai-doi-dau-ronaldo-tai-serie-a-176-191088.html\">Sao Roma kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4257","checkdouble":"191352"},{"date":"17:28 16/07","title":"H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 2 t\u00e2n binh ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 trong tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/5/he-lo-2-tan-binh-tiep-theo-se-duoc-barca-cong-bo-trong-tuan-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin cho bi\u1ebft CLB Barca s\u1ebd tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng hai t\u00e2n binh ti\u1ebfp theo trong tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, sau c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Arthur v\u00e0 Clement Lenglet.</h2><h2>Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Willian v\u00e0&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Adrien Rabiot</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian roi san nhuong vi tri cho Firmino\" title=\"Willian r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Firmino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/willian.JPG\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Barca s\u1ebd s\u1edbm ch\u1ed1t v\u1ee5 Willian ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">World Cup 2018 k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fac th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ed9n nh\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. V\u1edbi Barcelona, sau c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Arthur v\u00e0 Clement Lenglet, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo t\u1edd Don Balon, CLB Barcelona \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i r\u1ea5t kh\u1ea9n tr\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam hai t\u00e2n binh trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Chelsea Willian v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf trung t\u00e2m tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 PSG, Adrien Rabiot.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Willian, Barca \u0111ang t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea khi ch\u1ed3ng l\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u euro. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Barca c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rabiot t\u1eeb PSG. Nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng PSG \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Rabiot gia nh\u1eadp Blaugrana v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 50 tri\u1ec7u euro.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi th\u00f4ng tin Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Paul Pogba, theo t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo cho hay, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba - Mino Raiola \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Barcelona v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalan ngay trong H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Manchester. Ph\u00eda M.U c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4256","checkdouble":"191356"},{"date":"15:41 16/07","title":"Liverpool v\u00e0 Atletico \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/liverpool-va-atletico-dai-chien-vi-vida.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vida t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Croatia ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Domagoj Vida n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Domagoj Vida n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/liverpool-va-atletico-dai-chien-vi-vida.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vida (s\u1ed1 21) ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1i qua, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-phap-vs-croatia-421-191272.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia</span> trong tr\u1eadn World Cup 2018, binh \u0111o\u00e0n caro \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c thua thi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-4.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Dalic l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eabn khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o. Trung v\u1ec7 Domagoj Vida l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVida c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Lovren h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Subasic tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c. Vida x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool v\u00e0 Atletico mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Vida</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Besiktas chap nhan ban Vida neu nhan duoc 35 trieu euro\" title=\"Besiktas ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Vida n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 35 tri\u1ec7u euro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/be.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Besiktas ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Vida n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 35 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Vida c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Lovren. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 The Kop. V\u1edbi Atletico, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Vida nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Godin, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDomagoj Vida \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1 cho Besiktas, n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Liverpool v\u00e0 Atletico Madrid th\u00ec nh\u1eefng Sevilla, Everton v\u00e0 Leicester c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4255","checkdouble":"191350"},{"date":"16:19 16/07","title":"Luke Shaw s\u1ebd r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 n\u1ebfu...","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/luke-shaw-se-roi-mu-o-he-2018-neu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luke Shaw r\u1eddi MU n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang ESPN c\u1ee7a Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luke Shaw c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Luke Shaw th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Young, anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luke Shaw r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luke Shaw r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/19/Luke-Shaw-roi-MU-o-He-2018-neu-hinh-anh.PNG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luke Shaw c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nMourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nLuke Shaw r\u1eddi MU n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang ESPN c\u1ee7a Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nHi\u1ec7n Southampton, Everton v\u00e0 Tottenham l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t cho Luke Shaw</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t, n\u1ebfu Luke Shaw mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh anh ph\u1ea3i cho th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0a y\u00eau s\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho Luke Shaw\" title=\"Mourinho Luke Shaw\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/21/5-guong-mat-99-se-roi-mu-trong-he-nay.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y Luke Shaw r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Luke Shaw v\u1edbi M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y hai b\u00ean s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Shaw r\u1eddi Old Trafford trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nM.U \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dalot t\u1eeb Porto, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 19 tu\u1ed5i. Tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Young ho\u1eb7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Dalot l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu Shaw ra \u0111i Mourinho s\u1ebd mua th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-tu-choi-theo-duoi-danny-rose-vi-172-188402.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Rose c\u1ee7a Tottenham</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i do kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Ben Davies. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 Spurs \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4254","checkdouble":"191351"}]}